.8]}, {"text": "occur.", "bbox": [143.8, 721.0, 195.3, 741.8]}, {"text": "As discussed in note 2 to the consolidated financial statements (see “New Accounting Pronouncements-", "bbox": [185.5, 768.2, 1094.0, 789.0]}, {"text": "Leases”), we will adopt a new lease accounting standard on January 1, 2019. Upon adoption of the new standard,", "bbox": [143.8, 793.2, 1094.1, 814.0]}, {"text": "our operating leases will result in lease assets and lease liabilities being recognized on the balance sheet.", "bbox": [143.8, 818.2, 1015.6, 839.0]}, {"text": "Rent expense under all non-cancelable operating leases totaled $179, $160 and $149 for the years ended", "bbox": [185.5, 865.4, 1094.2, 886.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2018, 2017 and 2016, respectively.", "bbox": [143.8, 890.4, 558.4, 911.3]}, {"text": "Capital Leases", "bbox": [143.8, 948.5, 274.1, 969.3]}, {"text": "Capital lease obligations consist primarily of vehicle, building and equipment leases with periods expiring at", "bbox": [185.5, 984.7, 1094.1, 1005.6]}, {"text": "various dates through 2028. Capital lease obligations were $122 and $67 at December 31, 2018 and 2017,", "bbox": [143.8, 1009.7, 1094.2, 1030.6]}, {"text": "respectively. The following table presents capital lease financial statement information for the years ended", "bbox": [143.8, 1034.7, 1094.2, 1055.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2018, 2017 and 2016, except for balance sheet information, which is presented as of December 31,", "bbox": [143.8, 1059.7, 1094.2, 1080.6]}, {"text": "2018 and 2017:", "bbox": [143.8, 1084.8, 273.5, 1105.6]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [877.4, 1126.6, 910.8, 1143.3]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [950.4, 1126.6, 983.7, 1143.3]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [1019.2, 1126.6, 1052.5, 1143.3]}, {"text": "Depreciation of rental equipment . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 1157.0, 842.0, 1177.8]}, {"text": "$ 22", "bbox": [873.3, 1157.0, 915.0, 1177.8]}, {"text": "$ 21", "bbox": [946.